Algorithms

Class MultiCSV

  • java.lang.Object
    • Algorithms.MultiCSV

  • public class MultiCSV
extends java.lang.Object
    This class reads all the csv files from a folder and creates a new project. each layer in the project is one file the function read. each layer is made of elements and each element represents a point with metadata. The MultiCSV function will return a project and make a ksm file of all the data.
    Author:
    Alex Vaisman , Shay Naor.
